OL,3,CCould a blood test help predict and
OL,4,Cprevent future MND cases?
OL,6,FFormer welsh international Alix Popham
OL,7,Fhas been diagnosed with probable
OL,8,Fchronic traumatic encephalopathy and
OL,9,Fearly onset dementia.
OL,11,F"I used to live on pain killer, head
OL,12,Fache tablets," the retired rugby star,
OL,13,Fwho is co-founder of charity Head For
OL,14,FChange, told me.
OL,16,F"I've had anger explosions where I
OL,17,Fjust can't understand what's going on,
OL,18,Fand that's not been very nice for my
OL,19,Fthree children or Mel, my wife."
