OL,3,CCould a blood test help predict and
OL,4,Cprevent future MND cases?
OL,6,FResearchers at Durham University
OL,7,Fcompared blood samples from retired
OL,8,Fathletes.
OL,10,FIn those that had been concussed more
OL,11,Fthan five times during their playing
OL,12,Fcareer they found lower levels of a
OL,13,Fprotein called RBP-4 which is vital
OL,14,Ffor a healthy brain - and higher
OL,15,Flevels of a protein called tau, which
OL,16,Fis an indicator of
OL,18,Fconditions like Alzheimer's and MND.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
