OL,3,CCould a blood test help predict and
OL,4,Cprevent future MND cases?
OL,6,FIt was a relatively small sample, so
OL,7,Fisn't conclusive proof concussion
OL,8,Fcauses these conditions but does offer
OL,9,Fhope of spotting them sooner.
OL,11,FAcademics say that if blood can be
OL,12,Ftested and monitored for these
OL,13,Fspecific proteins, it may be possible
OL,14,Fto diagnose athletes early for
OL,15,Fneurodegenerative diseases and provide
OL,16,Fearly interventions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
