OL,3,CCould a blood test help predict and
OL,4,Cprevent future MND cases?
OL,6,FSenior author on the study, Professor
OL,7,FPaul Chazot, from Durham University's
OL,8,Fdepartment of biosciences, told me:
OL,9,F"Early diagnosis is reliant on good
OL,10,Fearly accurate biomarkers.
OL,12,F"The earlier you know the more chance
OL,13,Fof the current interventions actually
OL,14,Fmaking a difference."
OL,16,FThe researchers are trying to secure
OL,17,Ffunding to carry out a follow up study
OL,18,Fwith the players.
