OL,3,CCould a blood test help predict and
OL,4,Cprevent future MND cases?
OL,6,FCommenting on the study, Popham said:
OL,7,F"It's a huge positive and going in the
OL,8,Fright direction but we've got to make
OL,9,Fchanges now, because this blood test
OL,10,Fis maybe five or 10 years away, and
OL,11,Fthere's damage being done to current
OL,12,Fplayers everyday."
OL,14,FCures remain a way off but treatments
OL,15,Fare coming along - Popham finds ice
OL,16,Fbaths help quieten the pain in is
OL,17,Fbrain.
OL,19,FIn the future, the hope is others may
OL,20,Fbe able to get help before the
OL,21,Fsymptoms begin.
